name: Purple Clutch
description:
Perfect for going out day or night, this clutch is as practical as it is fashionable.  

Measuring approximately 11" wide & 5" high and lined with high-quality Ghanaian fabric, this purse includes a center divider, zipper pocket and smaller pockets sized to fit credit cards and cash.

Completely handmade by one of our seamstresses in Ghana, there is an inside label signed by the artist who made it.

Vegan (contains no animal product). Made from sustainable materials.

Due to the unique nature of the fabric patterns, each item may differ slightly from the image shown.
